        <abstract> 
<p>CD insistently requests JdeCS to have all rough illustrations [for <hi rend="italic">Fossil Cirripedia</hi> (Lepadidae)] done in time for next Council meeting of the Palaeontographical Society.</p> 
        </abstract>
